@page "/"

<PageTitle>ECommerce Home</PageTitle>

<div>
    <header class="w3-container w3-center w3-padding-32">
        <h1 class="w3-wide">ECommerce Example</h1>
        <p class="w3-opacity">
            <i>Microservices with Kafka: ECommerce Example (.NET 8)</i>
        </p>
    </header>

    <section>
        <img class="w3-image" src="https://th.airportels.asia/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/12/E-commerce-online-shopping.jpg"
             alt="E-Commerce Online Shopping" style="width:100%">
    </section>

    <section class="w3-container w3-center w3-content" style="max-width:600px; margin-top:20px;">
        <h2 class="w3-wide">About Us</h2>
        <p class="w3-justify">
            A sample e-commerce app using .NET 8. The frontend is built with Blazor Web App,
            while backend services are developed using Web API. Entity Framework Core with a code-first approach
            is used for database interactions, with SQL Server as the database. Additionally,
            Kafka serves as a message broker for asynchronous communication between services.
        </p>
    </section>
</div>

